{"id":2989,"date":"2025-06-05T13:37:47","date_gmt":"2025-06-05T06:37:47","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2989"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:19:19","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:19:19","slug":"nguyen-nhan-gay-mun-pho-bien","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/nguyen-nhan-gay-mun-pho-bien\/","title":{"rendered":"Hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00fang v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5n &#8211; Kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 10 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 &#8220;\u0111\u00e1nh bay&#8221; m\u1ee5n, b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang <strong>nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n.<\/strong> Khi hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 ngu\u1ed3n c\u01a1n, b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p x\u1eed l\u00fd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng GSC kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 10 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p nh\u1ea5t. C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p khoa h\u1ecdc gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1eb9p ngay trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phan-loai-mun-va-bieu-hien-cua-tung-tinh-trang-mun\"><\/span><b>Ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00f9y v\u00e0o t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n, l\u00e0n da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n qua nhi\u1ec1u tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng nh\u01b0 vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ecf, m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc m\u1ee7, ng\u1ee9a r\u00e1t ho\u1eb7c \u0111au nh\u1ee9c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Theo c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u, m\u1ee5n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu do s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i hormone khi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi vi khu\u1ea9n, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 b\u00edt t\u1eafc nang l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u00eam c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. D\u1ef1a tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea1ng, m\u1ed7i lo\u1ea1i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n ri\u00eang. C\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3772\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3772\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3772\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-1.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3772\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-khong-viem-mun-an\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng vi\u00eam\/ m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1? H\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh khi l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc b\u1edfi d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng kh\u00e9p k\u00edn, m\u1ee5n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng (m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng). N\u1ebfu l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng h\u1edf, m\u1ee5n s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u00e0u \u0111en (m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en). Lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam, g\u00e2y s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf, m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 ho\u1eb7c t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c n\u1ed1t c\u1ee9ng d\u01b0\u1edbi da, \u0111au nh\u1ee9c v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-dau-den\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en\u00a0<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng qua nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1m nh\u1ecf, m\u00e0u \u0111en ho\u1eb7c n\u00e2u, h\u01a1i nh\u00f4 l\u00ean tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da. M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y vi\u00eam hay \u0111au nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-boc-cystic-acne\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc (Cystic Acne)<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc? \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh do nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong da. M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn, s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf, ch\u1ee9a m\u1ee7 tr\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c v\u00e0ng, khi ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y \u0111au nh\u1ee9c. Lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o th\u00e2m ho\u1eb7c s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m n\u1ebfu x\u1eed l\u00fd sai c\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3773\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3773\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3773\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-2-3.webp\" alt=\"M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc (Cystic Acne)\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-2-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-2-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-2-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-2-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3773\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc (Cystic Acne)<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-viem-do\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ecf<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 c\u00e1c n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ecf, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ee7, t\u1eadp trung quanh v\u00f9ng m\u0169i, mi\u1ec7ng ho\u1eb7c m\u00e1. M\u1ee5n vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ecf g\u00e2y c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111au r\u00e1t v\u00e0 ng\u1ee9a ng\u00e1y, b\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u l\u00e0n da \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m nh\u1eb9.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"10-nguyen-nhan-gay-mun-tai-mat-ban-can-biet\"><\/span><b>10 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n t\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n \u1edf t\u1eebng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t ra sao? M\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 da li\u1ec5u m\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe b\u00ean trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh 4 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n ch\u00ednh g\u1ed3m: t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng do t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft v\u00e0 b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, da nhi\u1ec5m khu\u1ea9n, vi\u00eam da v\u00e0 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da sai c\u00e1ch, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 10 th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lo-chan-long-to\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng gi\u00e3n r\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 &#8220;c\u1eeda ng\u00f5&#8221; cho b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u00edch t\u1ee5 t\u1ea1o ra th\u00eam m\u1ed9t nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc, h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf v\u00f9ng m\u0169i &#8211; n\u01a1i ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3774\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3774\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3774\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-3-3.webp\" alt=\"L\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-3-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-3-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-3-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-3-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3774\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>L\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cham-soc-da-sai-cach\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da sai c\u00e1ch<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da kh\u00f4ng k\u1ef9, t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1eb7c b\u1ecf qua b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m da b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y k\u00edch th\u00edch tuy\u1ebfn d\u1ea7u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n, g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-bi-nhiem-khuan\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec5m khu\u1ea9n<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi khu\u1ea9n P.Acnes (Propionibacterium Acnes) s\u1ed1ng s\u00e2u trong nang l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. Khi da t\u00edch t\u1ee5 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu oxy, vi khu\u1ea9n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd sinh s\u00f4i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, g\u00e2y vi\u00eam, s\u01b0ng v\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u00edch m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc, m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi khu\u1ea9n Demodex c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 \u0111\u1ecf. <\/span><b>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y ra m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 do y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-tiet-nhieu-dau-nhon\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da ti\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da lu\u00f4n trong tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i b\u00f3ng d\u1ea7u, l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho vi khu\u1ea9n sinh s\u00f4i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng, m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam,&#8230; V\u00ec th\u1ebf, l\u00e0n da d\u1ea7u c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t nh\u1eddn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3775\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3775\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3775\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-4-2.webp\" alt=\"Da ti\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-4-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-4-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-4-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-4-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3775\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Da ti\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thay-doi-noi-tiet-to\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong c\u00e1c giai \u0111o\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 d\u1eady th\u00ec, h\u00e0nh kinh, mang thai,&#8230; l\u00e0m t\u0103ng sinh b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, khi\u1ebfn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1eb7p m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t, c\u1eb1m ho\u1eb7c l\u01b0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"te-bao-chet-tich-tu\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u00edch t\u1ee5<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3 khi\u1ebfn l\u1edbp da s\u1eebng h\u00f3a ch\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t, g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho m\u1ee5n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft 2\u20133 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 da lu\u00f4n s\u1ea1ch, tho\u00e1ng, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thoi-quen-sinh-hoat-xau\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00f3i quen sinh ho\u1ea1t x\u1ea5u<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ee9c khuya, ch\u1ea1m tay l\u00ean m\u1eb7t, t\u1ef1 \u00fd n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n hay l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da v\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u1ee5n th\u00eam tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng. Thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00f3i quen x\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"che-do-an-uong-khong-lanh-manh\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0102n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u tinh b\u1ed9t, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng (b\u00e1nh ng\u1ecdt, khoai t\u00e2y chi\u00ean) c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng huy\u1ebft, k\u00edch th\u00edch tuy\u1ebfn d\u1ea7u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e3y duy tr\u00ec ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n gi\u00e0u rau xanh, tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y v\u00e0 u\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 da kh\u1ecfe t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3776\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3776\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3776\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-5-2.webp\" alt=\"Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-5-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-5-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-5-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/22-5-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3776\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dung-my-pham-khong-phu-hop\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ch\u1ee9a corticoid ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9c h\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 l\u00ean m\u1ee5n \u1ed3 \u1ea1t. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m skincare kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i da (d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n, h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m) c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn da n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tac-dung-phu-cua-thuoc\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a thu\u1ed1c<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 thu\u1ed1c tr\u00e1nh thai, kh\u00e1ng sinh ho\u1eb7c kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n hormone, k\u00edch th\u00edch tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 da m\u1eb7t b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n khi ng\u1eebng d\u00f9ng thu\u1ed1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-cach-cham-soc-da-ngua-mun-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0n da lu\u00f4n s\u1ea1ch kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf m\u1ee5n quay l\u1ea1i, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t th\u00f3i quen ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da khoa h\u1ecdc. Hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 <\/span><b>nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da t\u1eeb trong ra ngo\u00e0i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn chi ti\u1ebft gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"giu-da-sach-sau-nhung-diu-nhe\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1eef da s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch: R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t 2 l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y &#8211; bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng sau khi th\u1ee9c d\u1eady v\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ng\u1ee7. Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ngay sau khi \u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n t\u00edch t\u1ee5. L\u01b0u \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n, h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o b\u1ecdt m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3755\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3755\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3755\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-4-2.webp\" alt=\"\u00c1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-4-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-4-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-4-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-4-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3755\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>\u00c1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t m\u1ea1nh: D\u00f9ng l\u1ef1c qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh khi r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t, t\u1ea9y trang hay t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1edbp bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho vi khu\u1ea9n x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khong-tu-y-nan-mun\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 \u00fd n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng <\/span><b>nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y ra m\u1ee5n ch\u00ednh<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0 t\u1ef1 n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n. Vi\u1ec7c t\u1ef1 n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 d\u1ec5 khi\u1ebfn vi khu\u1ea9n l\u00e2y lan, l\u00e0m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ebfn spa ho\u1eb7c c\u01a1 s\u1edf da li\u1ec5u uy t\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dung-my-pham-lanh-tinh-khong-gay-bit-tac-lo-chan-long\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u01afu ti\u00ean c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m skincare c\u00f3 nh\u00e3n &#8220;non-comedogenic&#8221; (kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n), kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a d\u1ea7u, c\u1ed3n, paraben hay h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng, gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"uong-du-nuoc-moi-ngay\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">U\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 2 l\u00edt n\u01b0\u1edbc\/ng\u00e0y gi\u00fap da duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e0o th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1 v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba. Da \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ebd h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf ti\u1ebft b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"an-uong-khoa-hoc-giam-thuc-pham-gay-mun\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0102n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc, gi\u1ea3m th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3756\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3756\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3756\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3756\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0103n rau xanh, tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y t\u01b0\u01a1i, c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1t v\u00e0 ng\u0169 c\u1ed1c nguy\u00ean h\u1ea1t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tinh luy\u1ec7n, s\u1eefa v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o b\u00e3o h\u00f2a (b\u00e1nh ng\u1ecdt, khoai t\u00e2y chi\u00ean,&#8230;).<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bao-ve-da-khoi-anh-nang-mat-troi\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ee5n v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng! Tia UV c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi\u00eam v\u00e0 t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau m\u1ee5n. Ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho da m\u1ee5n v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF t\u1eeb 30 tr\u1edf l\u00ean, k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 nh\u00e3n &#8220;non-comedogenic&#8221;.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0i, \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p. Hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 <\/span><b>nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> v\u00e0 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng quy tr\u00ecnh skincare ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e0n da m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng, s\u1ea1ch m\u1ee5n. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean theo d\u00f5i chuy\u00ean m\u1ee5c ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a GSC \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00eam ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da h\u1eefu \u00edch nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p khoa h\u1ecdc gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1eb9p ngay trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":3771,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2989","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2989","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2989"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2989\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3977,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2989\/revisions\/3977"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3771"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2989"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2989"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2989"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}